description.action:
On the Qatar Airways baggage allowance page, the economy class baggage allowances are as follows: 
- Economy Lite: 20kg (44lb) 
- Economy Classic: 25kg (55lb) 
- Economy Convenience: 30kg (66lb) 
- Economy Comfort: 35kg (77lb). 
For flights to/from Africa or Americas, the allowance is 1 piece (23kg/50lb each). 
Hand baggage is 1 piece (7kg/15lb).
